{"tid":1701424,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「廿三條」張曉明指23條未立法 致「港獨」活動加劇","createTime":"2019-11-09T05:05:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T02:38:11.000Z","uid":172599,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"3e8a30896a6c749bc047ced9acd480263df59e57","tid":1701424,"uid":172599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:05:40.000Z","msg":"國務院港澳辦主任張曉明在《〈中共中央關於堅持和完善中國特色社會主義制度、推進國家治理體系和治理能力現代化若干重大問題的決定〉輔導讀本》中撰文，當中提到香港尚未完成基本法第23條立法，令「港獨」勢力活動加劇。<br />\n<br />\n張曉明指出，香港尚未完成基本法第23條立法，也未設立相應執行機構，這也是近幾年來「港獨」等本土激進分離勢力的活動不斷加劇的主要原因之一。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，建立健全維護國家安全的法律制度和執行機制，強化執法力量，已成為擺在香港特別行政區政府和社會各界人士面前的突出問題和緊迫任務。"},{"pid":"7c090bdc0f15f19e1cad89c9546e4d6998f6d8d2","tid":1701424,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:06:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">出門前入去rt + like + reply</span><br />\n（最新）Senator Rubio 出聲講議員被捕<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1192955446132387846\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1192955446132387846&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOKhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=90c97562\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1192955446132387846&h=d2de161b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1192955446132387846</a><br />\n仲有Senator Rubio都知道周同學死訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1192876824868671488?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1192876824868671488%3Fs%3D21&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOKhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=0f479215\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1192876824868671488%3Fs%3D21&h=c4dc6427\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1192876824868671488?s=21</a><br /